title: 820-3209-a no power, orange light
820-3209-a no power, orange light
message:
Post voltage on all big coils, if you get any.
Start with L7220 (5V_S3)..
First be sure to have 3V3_S5/SUS.

title: 820-3209-a no power, orange light
message:
" L7630 PPCPUVCCIO_S0_REG / PPCPUVCCIO_S0_REG_R 0V "
There is your problem.
First post diode mode to ground.
If short, lift L7630 one side and see where it remains.
If good, post voltage U7600, pins 3, 13, 14.
Be sure R/C7630 are good.
